                    "description": "In my current role I'm responsible for both up and downstream supply chain management. I take care of the category 'Winter sports' for the region South East Asia & Oceania. I am based out of Singapore.\n\nMAIN RESPONSIBILITIES\n\nCATEGORY MANAGEMENT\n- Writing a yearly strategy and business plan for the my sports in the region\n- Selecting the most profitable offer for the region based on historical data analysis, stake holder wishes and customer feedback\n- Working with merchandising to make the most efficient and commercial store layout\n- Supporting on- and offline business with commercial strategies \n\nSUPPLY\n- Reviewing yearly supply policy based on global supply context & business parameter\n- Responsible for balancing the KPIs product availability and stock lifetime whilst ensuring turnover growth and margin targets\n- Ensuring value creation through optimal stock management in a very complex region\n- Working with our procurement team to secure our upstream supply and optimal lead times\n- Supporting our retail team in having the quickest stock rotation through just in time replenishment",
                    "title": "Regional Category Manager & Supply Planner Winter Sports SEA-O",
                    "employment_type": "Full-time"
